Hmmm, that worked up a thurst. 
<br />
&lt;pulls out his ogre mug and fills it.&gt; 
<br />

<br />
<belches>
<br />

<br />
&lt;cocks an eye at his mug&gt; 
<br />

<br />
Ya never fergets th' past, but ya gotta look ta th' future. Everyone has th'r own hero's journey. There's many a dragon yet ta slay &lt;ponders&gt; n gnomes too.&lt;Thinks of Tufgut with an evil grin on his face&gt; Thr' always be time enuf ta tell yer tales ta th' young uns with sad wistful longing, when yer bones wont hold th' weight o yer armor n whackin stick. Ya seems ta me, a warrior yet worthy of many a foe yet ta be vanquished. N sometimes theres even topless KOA gals partyin in the fountain yet ta oogle.
<br />

<br />
Heh heh.
<br />

<br />
&lt;slightly slurred speech&gt;
<br />
Live Long KOA!!
<br />

<br />
&lt;Eyes glaze over&gt; 
<br />
&lt;Head falls forward over the mug and bubbles form as snoring sounds begin eminating from the ogre mug&gt;<br />_________________<br />The Queen's own Red Dwarf
